title: NFL ATL: Dolphins Brian Hartline & TNF preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Dolphins Brian Hartline & TNF preview
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling welcome Miami Dolphins wide receiver into Studio 66 where they talk about his season, fantasy football and old Jim Carrey movies. The crew also talks about the disappointing players this season and previews the “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the New York Giants and Chicago Bears. Also, find out which team the heroes ‘stick a fork in’ this season.  Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
